cff-version: 1.2.0
title: >-
  paleotopo-data-assimilation: an open framework for amplitude-corrected
  Phanerozoic paleotopography
message: >-
  If you use this software or the corrected Scotese & Wright PaleoDEMs
  produced by it, please cite both the methodology paper (Zhou, Müller &
  Farahbakhsh, in review) and the underlying mohometry paper (Zhou,
  Müller & Farahbakhsh, 2025).
type: software
authors:
